		<h1 class="uber-text text-center">Principals</h1>
		<h1>The Job</h1>
		<p>As we encounter situations in our lives, we need a solution which will carry us from where we are to where we want to be. This need for a solution which will resolve a situation is a job.</p>

		<p>Many jobs are timeless, but solutions for those job may not be. Consider the job of Getting important documents, quickly and safely, from one place to another.</p>
		<div class="text-center">
			<img src="images/2.a.-The-Job.png" alt="">
		</div>

		<p>Pharaohs hired couriers with homing pigeons, who walked along the Nile. President Roosevelt hiring the First Transcontinental Railroad, which used trains. A businessman hiring FedEx, which flies jet planes across the world.</p>
		
		<h4 class="text-center">Even though the job stayed the same for 2,000 years, the solution changed, becoming a better fit each time. </br>A job is place where solutions can fit.</h4>
