		<h1>Consideration Set</h1>
		<p>The solutions customers consider Hiring for a Job.</p>

		<p>When considering what to Hire for a Job, customers are thinking of ‘what will do the Job best’ and ‘what trade offs am I evaluating’. </p>

		<p>In this instance, they are building a Consideration Set. If their Job is to satisfy their hunger, they may consider a pizza...but also a deli sandwich, a burrito, sushi, or even nothing - preferring to wait for another opportunity to eat.</p>
